section.para:
For running the setup go to the gem's directory with .rvm/gems/ruby-2.2.1/gems/PublicanCreators- &pcver;
. Then just typerake setup.
Keep in mind, that the 2.2.1 from ruby-2.2.1 must match your chosen version. Also you have to replace &pcver; with the installed version of PublicanCreators.
